      "./src/assets/images/avatars/w-40s-4-100.webp",
    content:
      "Excellent experience. Same day service, friendly serviceman, very thorough and made sure to explain all the work done and equipment.",
  },
  {
    name: "George O.",
    role: "Palos Park",
    avatar:
      "./src/assets/images/avatars/m-50s-3-100.webp",
    content:
      "Brian was very professional and is great at what he does. We have had both Brian and Max several times and they were great. Would highly recommend them with your plumbing needs. ",
  },
]}
/>
 <Stats1 
    stats={[
      { id: 1, label: "Years in Business", value: "20+" },
      { id: 2, label: "of Happy Customers", value: "1000s" },
      { id: 3, label: "5-Star Reviews", value: "150+" },
      { id: 4, label: "Average Rating", value: "4.8/5" },
    ]}
  />
   
</section>

<section class="pad-sm">
 <Logos5
    heading="Trusted by Your Favorite Local Businesses"
    subheading="and nation-wide chains alike"
    logos={[
      {
        src: "./src/assets/images/logos/customer-logos/culvers-logo.webp",
        alt: "Culver's",
